display: Superior Attuned Superior Command of the Mastermind F
help: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character. Gives the Mastermind an aura that boosts the Area of Effect Defense of nearby henchmen and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.RechargeTime.Scale}%. This enhancement can only be slotted in a Mastermind pet power.
shortHelp: Set: Superior Command of the Mastermind
